@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor Client
participant "FastAPI" as API
participant "routers/predict.py" as Predict
participant "services/model_manager.py" as ModelMgr
participant "services/inference.py" as Infer
database "uploads/" as Uploads
database "outputs/" as Outputs

Client -> API: POST /predict/image
API -> Predict: route call
Predict -> Uploads: save uploaded file
Predict -> Predict: validate type and size
Predict -> Infer: run_inference(image, model_id)
Infer -> ModelMgr: get_model_info(model_id)
ModelMgr --> Infer: model metadata + YOLO instance
Infer --> Predict: prediction data
Predict -> Infer: draw_inference(image, pred, model_id)
Predict -> Outputs: write annotated image
Predict --> API: JSON result_url + prediction
API --> Client: response

@enduml
